@startuml c4_context
title C4 Level 1 — System context (Off-Campus Housing Tracker)
skinparam defaultFontName Helvetica
skinparam shadowing false

actor "Student / Landlord" as user
rectangle "Off-Campus Housing\nPlatform" as sys #LightSkyBlue

cloud "Email / SMS\nproviders" as notify_ext
cloud "Maps / embed APIs\n(optional)" as maps_ext
cloud "Object storage\n(MinIO / S3)" as storage_ext

user --> sys : HTTPS (webapp + API)
sys --> notify_ext : Notifications
sys --> maps_ext : Map previews
sys --> storage_ext : Media objects

note right of sys
  Event-driven microservices,
  per-service Postgres, Kafka KRaft.
end note

@enduml
